summary: February 1, 1985: Brown & Williamson Tobacco Corp. in Portland, Oregon. The company was founded in 1872. It is now called Brown, Williamson, & Co. (BBWCO) and is based at 600 Reisterstown Road, Suite "i208" in downtown Portland.
